file.content: {"openapi":"3.0.3","info":{"title":"Calculator Service","version":"1.0"},"servers":[{"url":"http://localhost:80","description":"Default server for calc"}],"paths":{"/add/{left}/{right}":{"get":{"tags":["calc"],"summary":"add calc","operationId":"calc#add","parameters":[{"name":"left","in":"path","description":"Left operand","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","description":"Left operand","example":1698882017578366363,"format":"int64"},"example":6747375795581831989},{"name":"right","in":"path","description":"Right operand","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","description":"Right operand","example":5855163322465186600,"format":"int64"},"example":1385266597691519195}],"responses":{"101":{"description":"Switching Protocols response.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"type":"integer","example":4212629202012168060,"format":"int64"},"example":686605435966370186}}}}}},"/swagger.json":{"get":{"tags":["calc"],"summary":"Download ../../gen/http/openapi.json","operationId":"calc#/swagger.json","responses":{"200":{"description":"File downloaded"}}}}},"components":{"schemas":{"AddStreamingBody":{"type":"object","properties":{"a":{"type":"integer","description":"Left operand","example":8803302123552712831,"format":"int64"},"b":{"type":"integer","description":"Right operand","example":5401762099778430809,"format":"int64"}},"example":{"a":1918630006328122782,"b":4288748512599820841},"required":["a","b"]}}},"tags":[{"name":"calc","description":"The calc service performs additions on numbers"}]}
